    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a stratospheric 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag six-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis remains in showroom state, with a verified crack-free rear subframe and factory-spec suspension kinematics. Finished in its original paint with flawless Nappa leather, this vehicle presents no mechanical compromises and offers the pure, tactile feedback of a legendary driver\u2019s machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
