      "description": "Presenting an exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a high-end ceramic coating; there are no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and tight, free of any bolster wear or fading, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, screen, and mechanical component operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records documented. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example of automotive excellence that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
